title: BESO
body: A passionate reggaeton track that showcases the smooth collaboration between ROSALÍA and Rauw Alejandro. The song blends traditional Spanish influences with modern urban beats.

title: Todo De Ti
body: An infectious Latin pop hit that dominated charts worldwide. Rauw Alejandro delivers catchy melodies with modern production that makes it impossible not to dance.

title: Desesperados
body: A vibrant collaboration that brings together reggaeton and pop elements. The chemistry between the artists creates an irresistible summer anthem.

title: Chantaje (feat. Maluma)
body: A seductive reggaeton track that became a global phenomenon. Shakira and Maluma's collaboration showcases perfect Latin rhythm and captivating vocals.

title: Hips Don't Lie (feat. Wyclef Jean)
body: An iconic fusion of Latin pop and hip-hop that became one of the best-selling singles of all time. Shakira's distinctive voice and rhythm are unforgettable.

title: Me Gustas Tú
body: A charming Latin pop song with catchy lyrics and upbeat rhythm. Manu Chao's distinctive style creates a feel-good anthem that's loved worldwide.

title: Tubarão Te Amo
body: A Brazilian funk hit that took social media by storm. The infectious beat and playful lyrics made it a viral sensation across Latin America.

title: Yo Voy (feat. Daddy Yankee)
body: A high-energy reggaeton collaboration that showcases both artists at their best. The track combines classic reggaeton elements with modern production.

title: Gasolina
body: The reggaeton anthem that introduced the genre to mainstream audiences worldwide. Daddy Yankee's iconic track remains a dancefloor filler decades later.

title: Del Mar
body: A smooth Latin track with oceanic vibes and romantic undertones. The melody captures the essence of summer love by the seaside.

title: Callaita
body: A reggaeton hit that showcases the new generation of Latin urban music. Bad Bunny and Tainy create a hypnotic rhythm that's both modern and catchy.

title: 1, 2, 3 (feat. Jason Derulo)
body: A cross-cultural collaboration that blends Latin rhythms with international pop appeal. The track showcases the global reach of Latin music.

title: Tú
body: A minimalist yet powerful track that showcases artistic depth. The simple title belies the complex emotions and beautiful production within.

title: Parado no Bailão
body: A Brazilian funk anthem that captures the energy of Rio's street parties. MC L da Vinte and MC Gury deliver infectious rhythms and party vibes.
artist: MC L da Vinte, MC Gury

title: Dinero
body: A collaboration between international stars that celebrates Latin music's global influence. Trinidad Cardona brings smooth vocals to this urban hit.

title: Copines
body: A French pop hit with Latin influences that showcases the international appeal of romance-themed music. Aya Nakamura's unique style shines through.

title: N'y pense plus
body: A melodic French track with Latin undertones. Tayc's smooth vocals create an atmosphere of romance and sophistication.

title: love nwantiti (feat. Dj Yo!)
body: An Afrobeats sensation that crossed over to Latin markets. The infectious rhythm and catchy hook made it a global phenomenon.

title: Monotonía
body: A powerful ballad that showcases vocal prowess and emotional depth. Shakira and Ozuna create a moving piece about love and relationships.

title: Baila Baila Baila - Remix
body: An energetic remix that transforms the original into a dancefloor anthem. The remix brings new life to an already catchy track.
